    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining onion </strong>finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 1,
