    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot (with a lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with your <strong>pork & beef mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!)</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
