      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince is beginning to brown, reduce the heat to medium high, then add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground coriander </strong>and<strong> chopped garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and<strong> half</strong> the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1707212710558-x200.jpg",
